      "content": "that's a good start. but it's a bit generic. can you make it more specific about why these progressive policies are actually dangerous? like, instead of just saying \"radical ideologies,\" talk about how they are actively destroying the nuclear family and why they are a threat to the survival of our way of life. make it feel like a real call to arms.",
